Note: If using GCC 7+, you may need to uncomment the indicated line at the top of the Makefile to disable select warnings.

To build manager and agent, run "make"
To build only the manager, run "make nm_mgr"
To build only the agent, run "make nm_agent"

To build the manager with MySQL support, specify -DMYSQL
To build the manager with NCURSES TUI support, specify -DNCURSES

For example, to build both applications with all optional features enabled:
   make NCURSES=1 MYSQL=1

